sellerAgent.name: Josh Kahn and Katie Busk Team

data.description: Welcome home! The 2 story entry foyer welcomes you into the bright living room and dining room combo with Palladian window and vaulted ceiling. At the back of the house, enjoy the open sightline from the kitchen, through the breakfast room into the family room with wood burning fireplace. The convenient main floor laundry and powder room round out the first floor. Upstairs you'll find a primary suite with separate tub and shower, dual sinks and walk-in closet. A full bath services the second and third bedrooms. The lower level is ready for your finishing! An extended two car garage provides plenty of storage. Take advantage of the warm weather on your concrete patio inside the fully fenced yard. Updates include: Roof (2015), Fence (2015), HVAC (2020). Take a stroll down to Green Pines Park or hop on the trail to downtown Wildwood. All in Award Winning Rockwood School district!
